{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784619688541,"sessionID":"ses_07c62e1e5ffemFsnADH4fVqMT5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_yU4nVututW9DEipfZQLxnU0e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"printenv OPENCODE_CONFIG_DIR SPECKIT_FANOUT_LINEAGE_ID SPECKIT_CLI_DISPATCH_STACK AI_SESSION_CHILD MK_SPEC_GATE_DISABLED","workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research"},"output":"(no output)","metadata":{"output":"(no output)","exit":1,"truncated":false},"title":"printenv OPENCODE_CONFIG_DIR SPECKIT_FANOUT_LINEAGE_ID SPECKIT_CLI_DISPATCH_STACK AI_SESSION_CHILD MK_SPEC_GATE_DISABLED","time":{"start":1784619688519,"end":1784619688540}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_053517bd052c5482016a5f22a836308191ba2470407db1ee12"}},"id":"prt_f839f6241001yC4rt2UJ8nEQ2V","sessionID":"ses_07c62e1e5ffemFsnADH4fVqMT5","messageID":"msg_f839ed9f10018QiRZhCEyosRRz"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784619688567,"sessionID":"ses_07c62e1e5ffemFsnADH4fVqMT5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_cXduMKEIgorBeQjKYtpxaiGN","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"ps -o pid,ppid,command= -p $$ -p $PPID","workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research"},"output":"  PID  PPID \n68644 68637 opencode run --model openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast --format json --dir /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research --variant high You are orchestrating the deep-research workflow YAML as a detached fan-out lineage.\\012This is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\\012Use the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\\012\\012\\012Read .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\\012  spec_folder: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/002-naming-manifests\\012  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/002-naming-manifests/research/lineages/sol-high-fast\\012  session_id: fanout-sol-high-fast-1784619539276-ffno9q\\012  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\\012  loop_type: research\\012  config.stopPolicy: max-iterations\\012  research_topic: Bring the styles backend into kebab-case conformance per filesystem-naming-convention.md by renaming _db, _engine, _harness, _manifest.json, _retrieval-manifest.json, and reconcile the two overlapping manifests (crawl _manifest.jso